    <rdfs:label>applicationFunctionalDomain</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">The functional domain of the Application for describing the organization’s activities from a system point of view.

Alignment:
- *tmforum*: the `noria:applicationFunctionalDomain` is equivalent to the *Domain* concept of the ODA Functional Framework.
</rdfs:comment>
