    <rdfs:label>Room</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A part of the physical world or a virtual world whose 3D spatial extent is bounded actually or theoretically, and provides for certain functions within the zone it is contained in.

Alignment:
- *BOT*: A Room is a specialization of a `bot:Space` for common sense understanding.
</rdfs:comment>
